What libraries are required?
============================

To run netyack, you need:
 * libcelt
 * libspeexdsp
 * libasound
 * libcrypt

Under Debian simply type:
# apt-get install libcelt0-0 libcelt-dev       \
                  libspeexdsp1 libspeexdsp-dev \
                  libasound2-dev libasound2

If the compiler somehow complains about not finding libspeexdsp1, try:
# ln -s /usr/lib/libspeexdsp.so.1 /usr/lib/libspeexdsp.so

Installation
============

$ make
# make install

Uninstall
=========

# make uninstall
$ make clean

